## Overview
This Power BI dashboard analyzes sales data across products, regions, and time. It helps visualize sales trends, performance by category, and top-performing regions and products.

## ðŸš€ Features
- KPIs: Total Sales, Order Count, Average Order Value
- Monthly Sales Trend (Line Chart)
- Sales by Region (Bar Chart)
- Sales by Product Category (Donut Chart)
- Top 5 Products by Sales (Bar)
- Interactive Filters: Date, Region, Category

